t": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229190, "content": "中国地区限量就会中国红和土豪金", "image": null, "praise_count": 787, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229446, "content": "LV2017夏季的名画系列？丑到发指", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2337}, {"id": 229191, "content": "本质上是常规产品贴了个贴纸变成了新包装再卖一次", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229447, "content": "纪梵希一七年限量款  本来就有的产品俩放一起装个合作就成限量了", "image": "img/option/option/20170814221744xIuOBqN9TJfCKHpr", "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104728}, {"id": 229192, "content": "秋冬限量是驼色大地色，春夏一定要薄荷绿糖果色", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229193, "content": "麦当劳小食盒，明明吃的都一样，印上小黄人就变成限量发售", "image": null, "praise_count": 279, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229449, "content": "纪念钞", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225977}, {"id": 229194, "content": "快消品牌联名款质量太差，懒得二次创作就说这是original design", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229450, "content": "明星款手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 671614}, {"id": 229195, "content": "周年纪念限量版，配方不变，瓶身花样很多：首次以典雅高贵的琥珀金奢华呈现，熠熠金属色泽不仅映衬出其中所蕴含的澎湃深海修护能量，更仿佛演绎着历经五十年的不朽传奇故事……", "image": null, "praise_count": 106, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 229451, "content": "众泰和北汽以及各种自主品牌推出的限量版车型，除了杀马特还是杀马特", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484602}, {"id": 269645, "content": "颜色不同，别的都一样", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641284}, {"id": 229455, "content": "yeezy的限定...白斑马都烂大街了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998837}, {"id": 231759, "content": "明明不高级，非要说自己高级。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089402}, {"id": 231761, "content": "TX的各种限量，总会再次出